SkillsDatabase
--------------
At the time of creating the shell of this application the following settings were used:

Ruby Version: 1.8.7 (universal-darwin10.0)
RubyGems Version: 1.3.7
Rails Version: 3.0.1
CouchDB Version: 1.0.1

Additional Installs
-------------------
NOT CURRENTLY USED: sudo gem install simply_stored (ActiveRecord style wrapper for couch with 6 total gems)

sudo gem install couchrest_model --pre (after which you may have to run "bundle update")




 
